Package com.commander4j.db

Class JDBMaterialType

java.lang.Object
com.commander4j.db.JDBMaterialType
public class JDBMaterialType
extends java.lang.Object
JDBMaterialType class is used to insert/update/delete records from the APP_MATERIAL_TYPE table. This table contains a list of valid types for a Material. A type is used to filter materials for reporting purposes.
